<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="author" content="JamSyck">
    <meta name="keywords" content="doaxvv, api, api rest, dead or alive, game, web">
    <meta name="description" content="A REST API for the Japanese game Dead Or Alive Xtreme Venus Vacation, showing detailed information about the girls.">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <meta property="og:title" content="DOAXVV API">
    <meta property="og:description" content="A REST API for the Japanese game Dead Or Alive Xtreme Venus Vacation.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://images2.imgbox.com/01/91/Zt9BDYCQ_o.jpg">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/icon.jpg" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/footer.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>DOAXVV API</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <div class="principal">
        <img src="/wallpaper.jpg">
        <h1>Dead Or Alive Xtreme Venus Vacation API</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="info">
        <p>Welcome to my REST API website for my favorite game, DOAXVV. Here I aim to provide you with all the information possible about each of the girls so you can get all this data and use it to build your own app with this data.</p>
        <br>
        <p>The API contains 30 current girls in-game, with a wide variety of string data and multimedia content.</p>
        <br>
        <h5>TRAILER:</h5>
        <div class="ratio ratio-16x9">
            <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/l3xYJJiESsU?si=lCUGVboeHVeCcaEc" frameborder="0"></iframe>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="title">CHARACTERS</h1>
    <main class="list">
        <% listchars.forEach(girl=>{ %>
            <div class="card-girl <%= girl.isBirthdayToday ? 'birthday' : '' %>">
                <div class="lc">
                    <img src="<%= girl.photo %>">
                </div>
                <div class="rc">
                    <h2><%= girl.name %></h2>
                    <i><%= girl.occupation %></i>
                    <p><%= girl.age %> years</p>
                    <a href="/character/<%= girl.id %>">Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        <% }) %>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>